---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { socialLinks } from "../config";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---



<Base>
  <section>
    <a href={socialLinks.twitter} target="_blank">
      <Image
        src="/profile.webp"
        alt="Profile photo"
        class="rounded-full bg-gray-100 block lg:mt-5 mt-0 lg:mb-5 mb-5 mx-auto sm:float-right sm:ml-5 sm:mb-5 grayscale hover:grayscale-0"
        width={160}
        height={160}
      />
    </a>

    <script>
            function me_when() {
                var a = new Date(2004, 6, 15);
                var b = new Date();
                var c = b - a;
                var d = c / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24 * 365.25);
                document.getElementById('my_age').innerHTML = '' + Math.floor(d) + '.' + (d % 1).toFixed(9).substr(2);
            }
            setInterval(me_when, 1);

    </script>

    <h1 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight">
        hi I'm K V <i><b>Varun</b></i> Krishnan
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert">
      <p>
      I'm a <span id="my_age"></span>       year old kid, trying to find meaning in life.
      </p>
      <p>
        During the days, there's a chance that you'll find me at <a href="https://mec.ac.in">Govt. Model Engineering College
        </a> and on weekends at <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/DsTQAUSdMrDeCnYk9">Kunnamkulam</a> or <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/EtzLbs5MBFVH5StGA">Kochi</a> in Kerala, India
      </p>

      <p>
        Professionally I mostly code in rust. You could see my works <a href="https://github.com/vrn21">here.</a>
        I'm currently interning at <a href="https://mecha.so">Mecha Systems </a>, where i'm helping the team build a debian based OS called <a href="https://github.com/mecha-org">MechanixOS</a>, for a <a href="https://mecha.so/comet">handheld linux computer</a>.
        I've also interned at <a href="https://fileago.com">FileAgo</a> where we were developing a client side FUSE application using <a href="https://github.com/dokan-dev/dokan-rust">dokan</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
      More about me, I used to <a href="/design">design</a>, a little bit of Option trading during the weekdays and Weekends for <a href="https://realmadrid.com">Los Blancos</a> ü§ç
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
